\">φόνοι, στάσεις, ἔρις, μάχαι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg007.perseus-grc1:1234\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ OC\">OC</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1234</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> (lyr.); <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἔριδες, νείκη, στάσις,..πόλεμος</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg008.perseus-grc1:788\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">788</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> ; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἔριδος ἀγών</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg003.perseus-grc1:1163\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Aj.\">Aj.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1163</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> (anap.); <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὅταν φίλοι φίλοισι συμβάλωσ᾽ ἔριν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0006.tlg003.perseus-grc1:521\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Med.\">Med.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">521</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> ; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἔριν περί τινος ἐκφυγεῖν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg034.perseus-grc1:736c\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lg.\">Lg.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">736c</biblScope